```bash
node --experimental-modules build/hermes-main.js test/basic
```

## Testing

Hermes tests uses mocha. See `test/suite`.

Hermes unit tests are run in the Android emulator (Emulator Pixel_3_API_28). The tests runs in `HermesTestsRunnerInstrumentation` class. Refer the screenshot below. A successful test must print a success message and no errors. 

![test output](test/suite/Output.png "Success Test Output")

## Building

```bash
yarn run clean:hermes
yarn run build:hermes
yarn run build
```

